  ('medical-tech-moex-01738', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有  關腎絲球體（glomeruli）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["有  孔洞的血管內皮細胞（fenestrated endothelial cells）可通透抗體", "腎  絲球體基底膜（glomerular basement membrane）位於血管內皮細胞與足細胞（podocytes）之間", "足  細胞（podocytes）又稱壁層上皮細胞（parietal epithelial cells）", "繫  膜細胞（mesangial cells）位於腎絲球體內的微血管之間的胞外基質，具收縮能力"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:04+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "72690637ac1c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1877a568bd87", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114090", "c": "308", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師中醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、1...", "original_question_number": 73, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
